{"tid":1943280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年3月25日，立法會通過「臨時潑款議案」...然後呢？","createTime":"2020-03-25T14:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T17:33:30.000Z","uid":345458,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"748e160fbe3989c00752c8e66f31465ae4047685","tid":1943280,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"然後，有班喪心病狂嘅癲狗一日間多咗2543隻同黨，6架新裝甲車，1部新水炮車，同埋數唔盡嘅催淚彈同電槍。<br />\n<br />\n...然後呢？<br />\n<br />\n然後一班為咗自己利益嘅泛民，<span style=\"color: red;\">仲唔肯初選，仲未有決心攬炒。</span><br />\n<br />\n我敢肯定，咁樣落去， 唔好話攬炒議會，最後一定連最基本35個黃絲議員都冇，<span style=\"color: red;\">相同嘅事情下年再發生一次，班癲狗繼續攞一大筆錢</span>，而且潑款會更加多。<br />\n<br />\n泛民究竟瞓醒未？初選又唔想搞，攬炒又唔肯，你哋究竟係咪想服務香港市民？"},{"pid":"cbf60a6f00f53a9146a61ff871f273c069f634d3","tid":1943280,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"初選只係第一步<br />\n初選完唔肯攬炒嘅一樣冇得留低"},{"pid":"55d0cfdf6e28a683f5bc565e9e11f009080ff0ef","tid":1943280,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf60a6f00f53a9146a61ff871f273c069f634d3","tid":1943280,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"初選只係第一步<br />\n初選完唔肯攬炒嘅一樣冇得留低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:50:58.000Z","msg":"連第一步都未達標<br />\n請大家繼續施壓"},{"pid":"09dbc5fdbb88547bf7d5d38e22b6907f5292b502","tid":1943280,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f838b654bf07380808462621d330608ce7074d3","tid":1943280,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"公民黨承諾支持協調機制及議會攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1943251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1943251</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n？？？"},{"pid":"0680b81c84eb1272724182bbffac9731703b6ff5","tid":1943280,"uid":912